#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/index.adoc:4
msgid ""
"Create: Factory Controller introduces a new block, the \"Factory "
"Controller\". It allows you to place factory gauges on a virtual board "
"stored in a single block, instead of having a wall of gauges in the game "
"world. The factory gauges are managed via a GUI. The mod adds many "
"enhancements to factory gauges, and some other components may also be placed "
"in factory controllers."
msgstr ""

